s=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">y</span></span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68\" class=\"mjx-mo\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size2-R\">)</span></span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-69\" class=\"mjx-mi MJXc-space1\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\">%</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-70\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\">7</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\">weekday=(13×month−15+year4+century4+day+year−2×century)%7</span></span></pre>\r\nTrong đó ta có:\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Ký hiệu</th>\r\n<th>Mô tả</th>\r\n<th>Ví dụ</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span id=\"MathJax-Element-2-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" style=\"font-family: \'Noto Serif\', serif; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; text-indent: 0px; text-align: left; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 19.36px; letter-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; word-spacing: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 1px 0px; position: relative;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;w&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;e&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;e&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;k&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;d&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;a&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;y&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-71\" class=\"mjx-math\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-72\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-73\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">w</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-74\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">e</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-75\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">e</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-76\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">k</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-77\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">d</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-78\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">a</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-79\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">y</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\">weekday</span></span></td>\r\n<td>là thứ ngày mà chúng ta cần tìm</td>\r\n<td><code>0 = Chủ nhật</code>, <code>1 = Thứ 2</code>,...</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span id=\"MathJax-Element-3-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" style=\"font-family: \'Noto Serif\', serif; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; text-indent: 0px; text-align: left; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 19.36px; letter-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; word-spacing: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 1px 0px; position: relative;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;m&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;o&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;n&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;t&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;h&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-80\" class=\"mjx-math\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-81\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-82\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">m</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-83\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">o</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-84\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">n</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-85\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">t</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-86\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">h</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\">month</span></span></td>\r\n<td>là tháng chúng ta cần xét, giá trị <code>1</code> đến <code>12</code>, bắt đầu từ tháng <code>3</code></td>\r\n<td><code>Tháng 3 = 1</code>, <code>Tháng 4 = 2</code>,..., <code>Tháng 12 = 10</code>, <code>Tháng 1 = 11</code>, <code>Tháng 2 = 12</code></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span id=\"MathJax-Element-4-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" style=\"font-family: \'Noto Serif\', serif; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; text-indent: 0px; text-align: left; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 19.36px; letter-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; word-spacing: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 1px 0px; position: relative;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;d&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;a&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;y&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-87\" class=\"mjx-math\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-88\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-89\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">d</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-90\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">a</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\">y</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\">day</span></span></td>\r\n<td>là ngày chúng ta cần tính</td>\r\n<td>ngày 1, 2, 3,..., 29, 30, 31</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span id=\"MathJax-Element-5-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" style=\"font-family: \'Noto Serif\', serif; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; text-indent: 0px; text-align: left; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 19.36px; letter-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; word-spacing: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 1px 0px; position: relative;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/19